
<div class="row wrapper wrapper-content">



  <div class="banner-top row col-sm-12">
    <div class="banner col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2" style="background-image: url('/banner/banner.jpg');">
      <div class="title col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-2">
        Buy &amp; sell on your college campus
      </div>
    </div>   
  </div>

  <div class="select-school container row col-sm-12">
    <div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2 select-school">
      <div class="ibox-content">
        <div class="col-sm-offset-3">
          <h3>
            <div class="pin icon" style="display: inline-block; background-image: url('/banner/sprite-board.png'); width: 38px; height: 38px; background-position-y: -220px;"></div>
            <span class="content">Find Your College</span>
          </h3>
        </div>
        <form>

          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
              <div class="input-group">
              <%= select_tag :college, options_from_collection_for_select(College.order(name: :asc).all, :id, :name_with_abbr_and_city), class: "form-control", include_blank: true %>
               <span style="color: white;" class="input-group-btn"> <button type="button" id="go" style="background-color: #29aae1;" class="btn ?btn-success">Go!
              </button> </span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </form>
      </div>      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 why-love">
    <div class="col-sm-4 feature feature-1">
      <div style="background-image: url('/banner/feature-1.png'); min-height: 160px; background-repeat: no-repeat;"></div> 
      <div class="title"><h3>1. Post an Item</h3></div>
      <div class="words"><p>Posting an item is super simple. College textbooks, electronics, furniture, housing... you can easily find and post everything you need for college life.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 feature feature-2">
      <div style="background-image: url('/banner/feature-2.png'); min-height: 160px; background-repeat: no-repeat;"></div>
      <div class="title"><h3>2. Contact Poster</h3></div>
      <div class="words"><p>has stuff allows you to safely contact other posters by giving you the freedom to select what information others see about you. Trust, transparency &amp; community are top priorities for us!</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 feature feature-3">
      <div style="background-image: url('/banner/feature-3.png'); min-height: 160px; background-repeat: no-repeat; "></div>
      <div class="title"><h3>3. Buy, sell, rent, &amp; trade</h3></div>
      <div class="words"><p>has stuff brings students who are looking to buy and sell items together in one place. Our college classifieds website gives you all the features you need to make and save money.</p> </div>
    </div>

  </div>



</div>


<script>
  
$(document).ready(function() {

  $(".navbar .navbar-form").addClass("hidden");
  $(".navbar .navbar-nav.post").addClass("hidden");


  $("body").on("click", ".select-school button#go", function(e) {
    var params = { filters : { college_id: 1 } }
    $.get("/classifieds/", params, function(data) {
      console.log(data);
      window.location = "/classifieds";
    });

  });

  var transition_bg = function() {
    var bp = $(".banner").css("background-position-y").replace(/[^-\d\.]/g, '');
    var newbp = bp - 448;
    $(".banner").css("background-position-y", newbp+"px");
  };

  window.setInterval(transition_bg, 3500);

});

</script>



